SIMPLE: motherfucker
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: motherfucker
<hw>moth"er*fuck`er</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A person who is
deemed to be worthless or despicable; -- obscene and highly
offensive.</def> <mark>[vulgar slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> rotter, rat, skunk, stinker, bum, crumb, lowlife,
scum bag, cocksucker, mother.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Any object viewed as annoying or frustrating; --
usually used as an expression of anger.</def> <mark>[vulgar
slang]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mother Goose</ent>⟦br⟧
